reviewText: I will never order "Keeping up with the Kardashians" or The City...not my cup of tea.  The Kardashians are obnoxtious and spoiled brats
Love the dvd! I am a big time Kardashianaholic so of course i am satisfied with the product.  It took longer than usaul for it to arrive but all in all i am completely satisfied.

Most shows that have a short first and second season would package them together but not this one...Pretty sure season 1 and 2 are each 10 episodes which is about 3 hours. The 2 seasons really shoulve been put together but other then that its a fun show to watch
I love watching Keeping Up With The Kardashians.  I watch it on tv every sunday.  I have never seen it from the beginning. I bought season 1 and 2 at the same time. Can't wait to watch them.
I love Keeping Up with the Kardashians. It is my favorite show and I was so happy to finally get this season on DVD. It shipped super fast and was brand new just like they said. :)
I have enjoyed the show for the past couple of years. What I like the most is that this is a family that really cares about one another.

So I'll be the first to admit that season 1 is more entertaining than season 2...but I'll be completely honest here, this show could become the worst show on television and I'd still watch it. Luckily though, it's not the worst show on television. Season 2 is still great. The dvd however is lacking. Just as the first season on dvd, it is censored and lacking in extras. But for the price, I'd say it's worth the purchase.
This klan hit a slump this season...not that season one was oscar winning material but it was entertaining.

This is a fun family. They have fun together. Kourtney, Kim , and Khloe are three of the funnest women on the show. Although Khloe is my favorite. She is a kick ass kinda girl. She's the only one who has the guts to tell people like it is. In the end, It's purely fun entertainment!

A guilty pleasure show to watch on E!.  Aired spring of 2008.
Season 2.
Well, we get more episodes in the 2cd season.  The 1 that will tug at the heart strings is the last episode when they go to New Orleans & help a family out who lost their home in the 2005 Katrina storm.

No special extras.  A few deleted scenes & a video segment with Rob.

Now, here are the problems with it 1.  EPISODES ARE NOT UNCUT.  Come on.  The Girls Next Door DVD's are uncut they have nudity & language.  Why is this show NOT shown uncut?  I am very disappointed in that. 2.  This HORRIBLE & CHEAP DVD case/holder.  It has intentional HOLES IN IT ON BOTH FRONT & BACK  Cheap, stupid & THOUGHTLESS 3.  No commentary as well on the episodes

At lease it does have a chapter/episode list.  BUT, the 1st season DVD said the original air dates for the episodes  Season 2 does NOT

Let us hope the DVD for season 3 is better than this

Great value for the early seasons, if you like the Kardashians you will like this season.  It is so cool to see them when they first started filming and weren't super famous yet.  Better than the newest seasons.
LOVE IT
I haven't watched all of the episodes yet,but the first few were good. I have season one. Season two pretty much picked up where season 1 ended.

This season was for sure more entertaining than the first season. It came complete with an episode list which made it much more smooth to find episodes that i did or didn't want to watch.

Picks up right where Season One left off. The Kardashians are at it once again, doing one crazy, hilarious thing after another. It is up to Kris Jenner, as the matriarch of the family, to bring order to this chaos and remind the girls that love and family always come first.
Great DVD season I bought to watch since I didn't have E! When the 1st & 2nd seasons were showing on TV. Glad that I could catch up by watching the complete season DVD.
I loved it, just want I was looking for. I am very satisfied and very happy about this product, I received it on time. Thank You
This is a funny show.  I enjoy it so much.  I love reality T.V.  The Kardashians are so funny and this season was great!!!
this was a gift for my sister...She rates it a 5...i think it's a 1...but we all have different taste
Great dvd!!! I just began watching the Kardashians and I love this show!!!! In amazing condition!!! Thank you so so much!!!

Shipped the product (I bought three seasons at once) early, in pristine condition. Amazing first few seasons of the prominent K family that I became terribly addicted! Can't wait until the later seasons comes out in DVD!!!!
Love this show! My package arrived promptly and I watched the whole Season in one night :) will definitely be purchasing all of the other seasons as well!

I love the antics of these gals and laugh out loud at some of the stuff they get into.  Takes me back to a time when me, my sis and best friend got into similar hijinks.  Turn off the bad news and escape with girls who just wanna have fun and do.  Such fun and the fashions, hair, makeup add to the mix.  Enjoy.

I love the Kardashians. It's a guilty pleasure of mine. The DVD works great and the show is so entertaining to me. Love them. Would definitely recommend to others. The Kardashians get a bad rap, but if people would give them a chance they would see just how funny, charming and smart that family is.
I really enjoyed the episodes f this season. They were more meaningful instead of just exposure for publicity.

I like the Kardashians. Even with all the drudgery, arguments and conceitedness, they are a family. They teach us that no matter what life throws at you, family always comes first.

I have been Keeping up with the Kardashians and I do not regret it <3
